OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773389069
OL,3,CTeenager who died after collapsing in
OL,4,Cfootball match pictured for first time
OL,6,FA teenager who died after collapsing
OL,7,Fduring a football match in Oxford has
OL,8,Fbeen pictured for the first time.
OL,10,FOxford United held a one minute's
OL,11,Fsilence for their academy goalkeeper,
OL,12,FAmelia Aplin, 15, who passed away
OL,13,Fduring the match at the club's
OL,14,Ftraining centre in Horspath at the
OL,15,Fweekend.
OL,17,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,18,Fsports park - she was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital, but couldn't be saved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
