PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773389069
OL,3,CTeenager who died after collapsing in
OL,4,Cfootball match pictured for first time
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of the fixture, Oxford
OL,7,FUnited Head Coach Matt Bloomfield
OL,8,Fspoke of the heavy atmosphere at the
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,F"My heart is broken for her parents,"
OL,12,Fhe said. "It's been very sombre here
OL,13,Fand we have to make sure that we give
OL,14,FAmelia's friends and family all the
OL,15,Flove they need going through this
OL,16,Fterrible time."
OL,18,FThe Junior Premier League described
OL,19,FAmelia as a "bright light" and a
OL,20,F"leader".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
